    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="OCPP-1-6-Documentation-Collection"><a href="#OCPP-1-6-Documentation-Collection" class="headerlink" title="OCPP 1.6 Documentation Collection"></a>OCPP 1.6 Documentation Collection</h2><p><strong>In this page, you will find a collection of documents related to OCPP 1.6. Click on the links below to view the corresponding PDF files in a new tab.</strong></p><h3 id="OCPP-1-6-Edition-2"><a href="#OCPP-1-6-Edition-2" class="headerlink" title="OCPP 1.6 Edition 2"></a>OCPP 1.6 Edition 2</h3><p><a href="/files/ocpp-1.6_edition_2.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">ocpp-1.6_edition_2.pdf</a><br><em>Description:</em> The complete specification document for OCPP 1.6 Edition 2.</p><h3 id="OCPP-1-6-Errata-Sheet"><a href="#OCPP-1-6-Errata-Sheet" class="headerlink" title="OCPP 1.6 Errata Sheet"></a>OCPP 1.6 Errata Sheet</h3><p><a href="/files/ocpp-1.6-errata-sheet.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">ocpp-1.6-errata-sheet.pdf</a><br><em>Description:</em> The errata sheet for OCPP 1.6, listing known issues and corrections.</p><h3 id="OCPP-J-1-6-Errata-Sheet"><a href="#OCPP-J-1-6-Errata-Sheet" class="headerlink" title="OCPP-J 1.6 Errata Sheet"></a>OCPP-J 1.6 Errata Sheet</h3><p><a href="/files/ocpp-j-1.6-errata-sheet.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">ocpp-j-1.6-errata-sheet.pdf</a><br><em>Description:</em> The errata sheet for OCPP-J 1.6.</p><h3 id="OCPP-J-1-6-Specification"><a href="#OCPP-J-1-6-Specification" class="headerlink" title="OCPP-J 1.6 Specification"></a>OCPP-J 1.6 Specification</h3><p><a href="/files/ocpp-j-1.6-specification.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">ocpp-j-1.6-specification.pdf</a><br><em>Description:</em> The detailed specification document for OCPP-J 1.6.</p><h3 id="OCPP-S-1-6-Errata-Sheet"><a href="#OCPP-S-1-6-Errata-Sheet" class="headerlink" title="OCPP-S 1.6 Errata Sheet"></a>OCPP-S 1.6 Errata Sheet</h3><p><a href="/files/ocpp-s-1.6-errata-sheet.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">ocpp-s-1.6-errata-sheet.pdf</a><br><em>Description:</em> The errata sheet for OCPP-S 1.6.</p><h3 id="OCPP-S-1-6-Specification"><a href="#OCPP-S-1-6-Specification" class="headerlink" title="OCPP-S 1.6 Specification"></a>OCPP-S 1.6 Specification</h3><p><a href="/files/ocpp-s-1.6-specification.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">ocpp-s-1.6-specification.pdf</a><br><em>Description:</em> The detailed specification document for OCPP-S 1.6.</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
